{"tid":800645,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(超越香港) 暴雨襲珠三角 深圳鬧市變汪洋 LV成孤島","createTime":"2018-08-31T04:52:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T04:25:02.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fa2addc6b1923639f87b11460eef152ff742df75","tid":800645,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T04:52:06.000Z","msg":"廣東多地自昨日開始出現連場暴雨，毗鄰香港的深圳遭遇大水，羅湖、龍崗及寶安區多個鬧市地段變成汪洋，汽車要破浪前進，有民眾更要用橡皮艇出入。有民眾抱怨排水等關鍵市政設施太差勁。<br />\n<br />\n首次連續兩日出現大暴雨、局地特大暴雨<br />\n<br />\n深圳市多地昨天至今日遭遇特大暴雨，發出暴雨紅色預警，全市中小學幼兒園停課。深圳气象局官方微博@深圳天氣稱，這是深圳有氣象歷史記錄以來首次連續兩日出現大暴雨、局地特大暴雨。其中龍崗區布吉24小時雨量達414.1mm，突破1952年8月以來極值。<br />\n<br />\n深圳當局凌晨通知香港，深圳水庫在凌晨排洪，香港政府相關部門包括北區民政事務處，渠務署、警務處和消防處等，採取跟進措施，防止新界地區可能出現水浸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2150000/2150077/700ffdbbgy1furjs3hzy0j20p20ka42p_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2150000%2F2150077%2F700ffdbbgy1furjs3hzy0j20p20ka42p_1024.jpg&h=cf9b6f8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 萬象城LV被洪水圍困。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2150000/2150077/1535593799_c8ea_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2150000%2F2150077%2F1535593799_c8ea_1024.jpg&h=0c872030&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 深圳多處水浸，地鐵站口變水塘。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2150000/2150077/12332_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2150000%2F2150077%2F12332_1024.jpg&h=fa466801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 深圳多處水浸，汽車沒頂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而在暴雨下，深圳多地出現嚴重水浸。當中位於羅湖的深圳萬象城周圍道路被水淹，讓萬象城變成「孤島」，車輛要涉水而過。有地鐵站口積水關閉。<br />\n<br />\n救援人員用救生艇運送民眾<br />\n<br />\n而深圳市龍崗區溪湧金海灘度假村路段發生路塌，龍崗轄區一處圍牆倒塌壓壞5輛車，幸無人員傷亡；在沙井萬豐村等區域，因水浸嚴重已斷電，有救援人員使用救生艇將民眾送往安全地區。<br />\n<br />\n除了深圳，中山新會、東莞、惠州惠東等珠三角地區，也發出暴雨紅色預警，幼兒園、中小學、中等職業等學校停課。中山三鄉嚴重水浸，多個小區停車場注滿水，多架車輛被浸。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2150077/%E6%9A%B4%E9%9B%A8%E8%A5%B2%E7%8F%A0%E4%B8%89%E8%A7%92%20%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E9%AC%A7%E5%B8%82%E8%AE%8A%E6%B1%AA%E6%B4%8B%20LV%E6%88%90%E5%AD%A4%E5%B3%B6%EF%BC%88%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87%EF%BC%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2150077%2F%25E6%259A%25B4%25E9%259B%25A8%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E7%258F%25A0%25E4%25B8%2589%25E8%25A7%2592%2520%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E5%259C%25B3%25E9%25AC%25A7%25E5%25B8%2582%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%25B1%25AA%25E6%25B4%258B%2520LV%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%25AD%25A4%25E5%25B3%25B6%25EF%25BC%2588%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2589%2587%25EF%25BC%2589&d=2w%2Bf58oZeIvkdAHGcO9PK%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=7f0d18b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2150077/%E6%9A%B4%E9%9B%A8%E8%A5%B2%E7%8F%A0%E4%B8%89%E8%A7%92%20%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E9%AC%A7%E5%B8%82%E8%AE%8A%E6%B1%AA%E6%B4%8B%20LV%E6%88%90%E5%AD%A4%E5%B3%B6%EF%BC%88%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87%EF%BC%89</a>"},{"pid":"eb2d9ba84dc1686e6dfa0040ec3f68f84c218661","tid":800645,"uid":76705,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T05:20:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/132051_6c91cf618b58e68845679129bf51c584.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F132051_6c91cf618b58e68845679129bf51c584.png&h=7076103a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11c9902ab5f52569f5a1416935150ffcb7d35ce2","tid":800645,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T05:25:29.000Z","msg":"中國第一科技城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ebba30a8313fc51cc70450607d9207262e33cf","tid":800645,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T05:28:44.000Z","msg":"又要漏電電死人了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afeb2c583f58b1bbf3f28abbfb1ef4e93011a46b","tid":800645,"uid":95,"lik